 0749        {

 0753                    ResetDisplayPanelToDefaults(currentTab);

 0763                    break;
 764                case "tabOthers":
 0765                    ResetOthersPanelToDefaults(currentTab);
 0766                    break;
 767                case "tabBrowsers":
 0768                    ResetBrowsersPanelToDefaults(currentTab);
 0769                    break;
 770                case "tabAutoURLs":
 0771                    ResetAutoURLsPanelToDefaults(currentTab);
 0772                    break;
 773                case "tabProtocols":
 0774                    ResetProtocolsPanelToDefaults(currentTab);
 0775                    break;
 776
 777                default:
 0778                    Logger.LogInfo("OptionsForm.ResetCurrentPanelToDefaults", $": {currentTab.Name}");
 0779                    break;
 780            }
 0781        }

 1069        /// <summary>
 1070        /// 
 1071        /// </summary>
 1072        private void LoadSettings()
 01073        {
 01074            Logger.LogInfo("OptionsForm.LoadSettings", "Start");
 1075
 1076            try
 01077            {
 1078                // 
 01079                _mBrowser.Clear();
 01080                var defaultBrowserGuid = _settings.DefaultBrowserGuid;
 01081                var listView = Controls.Find("lstBrowsers", true).FirstOrDefault() as ListView;
 01082                if (listView != null) listView.Items.Clear();
 1083
 01084                if (_imBrowserIcons != null) _imBrowserIcons.Images.Clear();
 1085
 01086                foreach (var browser in _settings.Browsers)
 01087                {

 01089                    _mBrowser.Add(_mBrowser.Count, clonedBrowser);
 1090
 1091                    // 
 01092                    bool isDefault = (defaultBrowserGuid == browser.Guid);
 1093
 1094                    // ListView
 01095                    if (listView != null)
 01096                    {

 01098                        item.Tag = _mBrowser.Count - 1;
 01099                        item.SubItems.Add(clonedBrowser.Target); // Target column
 01100                                        item.SubItems.Add(clonedBrowser.Y.ToString());
 01101                item.SubItems.Add(clonedBrowser.X.ToString());
 01102                        item.SubItems.Add(clonedBrowser.Hotkey.ToString());
 01103                        item.SubItems.Add(clonedBrowser.Arguments); // Arguments column
 01104                    }
 1105
 1106                    // ImageList
 01107                    if (_imBrowserIcons != null)
 01108                    {
 01109                        var image = ImageUtilities.GetImage(clonedBrowser, false);
 01110                        if (image != null)
 01111                        {
 01112                            _imBrowserIcons.Images.Add(image);
 01113                        }
 01114                    }
 01115                }
 01116                _mLastBrowserID = _mBrowser.Count - 1;
 1117
 1118                // 
 01119                _mProtocols.Clear();
